measure.CatchLine: Establishes Healthy Homes Program within the Oregon Health Authority to provide grants to entities to provide financial assistance to low income households and landlords.
measure.MeasureSummary:
Establishes Healthy Homes Program within the Oregon Health Authority to provide grants to entities to provide financial assistance to low income households and landlords. 
	Establishes Healthy Homes Repair Fund. 
	Establishes Interagency Task Force on Healthy Homes. 
	Takes effect on 91st day following adjournment sine die.
measure.RelatingToFull: Relating to healthy homes; and prescribing an effective date.
measure.RelatingTo: Relating to healthy homes; and prescribing an effective date.

Recommendation: Do pass with amendments and be printed B-Engrossed.

Recommendation: Do pass the B-Eng. bill.
Rules suspended. Third reading.  Carried by Lieber.  Passed.
historyActions.VoteText: Ayes, 23; Nays, 4--Boquist, Linthicum, Robinson, Thomsen; Excused, 3--Hansell, Heard, Manning Jr.
